des: "The first time I had this I was out camping with my best friend and her family. This is quick, easy and good! You can add more or take away ingredients to fit your taste."
ins: Heat a skillet over medium heat. Cook eggs in hot skillet, stirring vigorously, until they are beginning to solidify, 1 to 2 minutes. Stir hot dog slices and hash browns to eggs; cook and stir until the potatoes are browned and the eggs completely cooked, 3 to 5 minutes. Top with ketchup to serve.
